text: Younus Soomro is a Pakistani cardiologist and former caretaker minister. He was the Minister for Housing and Works in Khoso caretaker ministry in 2013. He is the grandson of the former Chief Minister of Sindh Allah Bux Soomro. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cardiologists Category:Federal ministers of Pakistan Younus Category:People from Shikarpur District Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
